Terrorsaur:



Terrorsaur leaned his body back, hearing a noise outside. He narrowed 
an optic and ran towards the mouth of the cave, with his gun in hand. 
He pointed his weapon out, and saw a pod and a bot outside. He slowly 
lowered it. "Who are you?" he asked the new bot.
